Invocation Name: the progression point podcast
des:
Welcome to The Progression Point Podcast.

Cory Curry and Ty Banks are your host.

Here on The Progression Point Podcast we'll be sharing with you Real-life stories of two guys living life from a place of "How Come" to a place of "How to" in order to make progress in every area of their lives.

In addition, we will be providing weekly #ProgressionPoints on how you as a listener can best implement the next steps needed towards making progress in your own life.

#progressoverperfection
